results.name: Let f(0) = 1, f(1) = 12, f(2) = 223, f(3) = 3334, f(4) = 44445, f(5) = 555556, etc. Sequence gives limiting value of f(0), f(f(0)), f(f(f(0))), ...
comment: The positions where 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, . . . appear are 1, 2, 5, 15, 52, . . . (Bell numbers A000110).
xref: Cf. A085693, A000110, A048993 = the number of occurrences of k in n-th block.
results.author: _Philippe Deléham_, Aug 14, 2003; extended Jun 10 2005
